{"pageid":30044,"pagename":"Magic stone (Tears of Guthix)","title":"Magic stone (Tears of Guthix)","displaytitle":"Magic stone (Tears of Guthix)","revid":14186511,"redirects":["Magic stone (Tears of Guthix","Magic stone (tears of guthix)"],"properties":[{"name":"smw-semanticdata-status","value":""},{"name":"page_image_free","value":"Magic_stone_(Tears_of_Guthix)_detail.png"},{"name":"description","value":"Magic stone is used in the quest Tears of Guthix to make the stone bowl. It is mined from rocks near Juna within the Magic stone mine. You must have a sapphire lantern with you to access the stones. Use the sapphire lantern on a light creature and select to go \"across the chasm\" and you will see the ores ahead. Without starting the Tears of Guthix quest, one can still mine the stone, but upon completing the quest it becomes unobtainable (along with the ability to craft stone bowls). The stone can be kept after the quest by dropping one before completing the quest and picking it back up after completing the quest."}],"content":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"noexcerpt noprint nomobile navigation-not-searchable rs-external-header-links\" style=\"display:none\"><span class=\"rs-header-icon rs-header-icon-rs\" data-text=\"RuneScape\" data-title=\"The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on Magic stone (Tears of Guthix).\" data-site=\"rs\">The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: <a href=\"https://runescape.wiki/w/Magic_stone_(Tears_of_Guthix)\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"rsw:Magic stone (Tears of Guthix)\">rsw:Magic stone (Tears of Guthix)</a></span></div>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\">This article is about the Magic stone used in Tears of Guthix. For the Magic stone used in Construction, see <a href=\"/w/Magic_stone\" title=\"Magic stone\">Magic stone</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox infobox-item\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-header\">Magic stone</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\