td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Value\" title=\"Value\">Value</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">1 coin</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/High_Level_Alchemy\" title=\"High Level Alchemy\">High alch</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">0 coins</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Low_Level_Alchemy\" title=\"Low Level Alchemy\">Low alch</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">0 coins</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Weight\" title=\"Weight\">Weight</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">2.267 kg</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><th colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-subheader\">Advanced data</th></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><th colspan=\"7\">Item ID</th><td colspan=\"13\">4703</td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"infobox-smw-data\" style=\"display:none\"></div>\n<div class=\"floatleft\"><a href=\"/w/File:Magic_stone_(Tears_of_Guthix)_detail.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Magic stone (Tears of Guthix) detail.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/Magic_stone_%28Tears_of_Guthix%29_detail.png/150px-Magic_stone_%28Tears_of_Guthix%29_detail.png?1fb79\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"150\" height=\"149\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Magic_stone_%28Tears_of_Guthix%29_detail.png/225px-Magic_stone_%28Tears_of_Guthix%29_detail.png?1fb79 1.5x, /images/thumb/Magic_stone_%28Tears_of_Guthix%29_detail.png/300px-Magic_stone_%28Tears_of_Guthix%29_detail.png?1fb79 2x\" data-file-width=\"1046\" data-file-height=\"1042\" /></a></div>\n<p><b>Magic stone</b> is used in the quest <a href=\"/w/Tears_of_Guthix\" title=\"Tears of Guthix\">Tears of Guthix</a> to make the <a href=\"/w/Stone_bowl\" title=\"Stone bowl\">stone bowl</a>. It is mined from rocks near <a href=\"/w/Juna\" title=\"Juna\">Juna</a> within the Magic stone mine. You must have a <a href=\"/w/Sapphire_lantern\" title=\"Sapphire lantern\">sapphire lantern</a> with you to access the stones. Use the sapphire lantern on a <a href=\"/w/Light_creature\" title=\"Light creature\">light creature</a> and select to go \"across the chasm\" and you will see the ores ahead. Without starting the Tears of Guthix quest, one can still mine the stone, but upon completing the quest it becomes unobtainable (along with the ability to craft stone bowls). The stone can be kept after the quest by dropping one before completing the quest and picking it back up after completing the quest.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Changes\">Changes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Magic_stone_(Tears_of_Guthix)?section=1&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Changes\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Magic_stone_(Tears_of_Guthix)?action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Changes\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable mw-collapsible sortable\" style=\"max-width:800px\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Date\n</th>\n<th class=\"unsortable\">Changes\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td data-sort-value=\"24 July 2007\"><a href=\"/w/24_July\" title=\"24 July\">24&#160;July</a>&#160;<a href=\"/w/2007\" title=\"2007\">2007</a><br />(<a href=\"/w/Update:King%27s_Ransom\" title=\"Update:King&#39;s Ransom\">update</a>)\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>The item was graphically updated.\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gallery_(historical)\">Gallery (historical)</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Magic_stone_(Tears_of_Guthix)?section=2&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Gallery (historical)\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Magic_stone_(Tears_of_Guthix)?action=edit&amp;section=